  },
  {
   "start": 70.72,
   "end": 73.08,
   "text": "Take your shoes off before you come in my house."
  },
  {
   "start": 76.08,
   "end": 84.88,
   "text": "So, put the table up, and I guess I shall give you a V-LOG of what I did."
  },
  {
   "start": 84.88,
   "end": 89.32,
   "text": "So, V-LOG, living in Van V-LOG."
  },
  {
   "start": 90.64,
   "end": 94.56,
   "text": "Um, yes, I left the house today."
  },
  {
   "start": 95.3,
   "end": 100.24,
   "text": "Um, my mom suddenly kicked me out, pretty much."
  },
  {
   "start": 100.24,
   "end": 105.66,
   "text": "Um, the first words out of her mouth about two days ago were, you've overstayed, you're welcome."
  },
  {
   "start": 105.66,
   "end": 106.64,
   "text": "I was like, oh."
  },
  {
   "start": 106.64,
   "end": 117.14,
   "text": "Um, so, uh, so first she was like, you stay with your brother, and then I was like, hmm, but then I was like, no, I think I'll just get a move on and do my road trip."
  },
  {
   "start": 117.14,
   "end": 122.04,
   "text": "So, um, here we are on the side of the road."
  },
  {
   "start": 122.1,
   "end": 124.82,
   "text": "I'm on the side of the road because the car broke down."
  },
  {
   "start": 124.82,
   "end": 127.82,
   "text": "Um, and I'm waiting for the tow truck to come."
  },
  {
   "start": 127.82,
   "end": 132.68,
   "text": "Um, lady called about five or ten minutes ago and said it would be a half hour."
  },
  {
   "start": 132.68,
   "end": 139.32,
   "text": "So, I guess they're going to tow it to Hayes, Kansas, and then I have it fixed."
  },
  {
   "start": 139.8,
   "end": 143.92,
   "text": "I was driving down the road, and I felt this snap and this vibration right at my feet."
  },
  {
   "start": 144.14,
   "end": 150.78,
   "text": "So, the, uh, and then the car just lost power, so, uh, the, uh, the throttle cable broke."
  },
  {
   "start": 151.72,
   "end": 155.36,
   "text": "So, at least it's not a big deal, but, and I have AAA, so."
  },
  {
   "start": 156.2,
   "end": 159.06,
   "text": "And I get to hang out here in the middle of the greenery."
  },
  {
   "start": 159.18,
   "end": 160.34,
   "text": "Look how green this is."
  },
  {
   "start": 160.82,
   "end": 162.02,
   "text": "This is what I love about my van."
  },
  {
   "start": 162.02,
   "end": 167.52,
   "text": "Like, I can be, um, you know, I can be in the middle of, like, beautiful nature, like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 167.56,
   "end": 169.04,
   "text": "Right at my doorstep like that, you know?"
  },
  {
   "start": 170.02,
   "end": 173.6,
   "text": "But inside, it's a cozy house at all times."
  },
  {
   "start": 173.74,
   "end": 174.34,
   "text": "It's great."
  },
  {
   "start": 174.42,
   "end": 177.46,
   "text": "You even have the pop-up up there and the bed and your music."
  },
  {
   "start": 177.64,
   "end": 180.36,
   "text": "It's a little storage area back here."
  },
  {
   "start": 180.62,
   "end": 181.02,
   "text": "It's badass."
  },
  {
   "start": 182.62,
   "end": 184.68,
   "text": "So, anyways, so what have I been doing?"
  },
  {
   "start": 184.68,
   "end": 195.56,
   "text": "So, the last time I did speaking video was when I, I was Hitler about two months ago, and then before that, yes, we had to be like, I've been in my house."
  },
  {
   "start": 195.7,
   "end": 196.74,
   "text": "I've been in my mom's house."
  },
  {
   "start": 196.8,
   "end": 199.46,
   "text": "I've been there for, uh, four months."
  },
  {
   "start": 200.4,
   "end": 201.08,
   "text": "I was there."
  },
  {
   "start": 201.16,
   "end": 202.7,
   "text": "I got there at the beginning of, uh, February."
  },
  {
   "start": 203.68,
   "end": 208.46,
   "text": "And, um, when I first got there, she was like, yeah, you'll be here probably a month."
  },
  {
   "start": 209.0,
   "end": 212.9,
   "text": "And I was there for, I could have been there a month as far as preparing for my kayak trip and stuff."
  },
  {
   "start": 212.9,
   "end": 221.14,
   "text": "But, I had a look at my personal website, and I was like, and I looked at all the pages, and I realized that I never finished any of them."
  },
  {
   "start": 221.42,
   "end": 225.4,
   "text": "Like, it was just this whole collection of all these unfinished pages."
  },
  {
   "start": 226.68,
   "end": 236.9,
   "text": "So, but it was fun for me to kind of, um, fix them all and make them all look, um, um, standard."
  },
  {
   "start": 237.4,
   "end": 238.12,
   "text": "Standardize them all."
  },
  {
   "start": 238.6,
   "end": 240.9,
   "text": "So, and I think I found my voice."
  },
  {
   "start": 240.9,
   "end": 246.16,
   "text": "I think I found, like, the, uh, the, uh, website design that I love."
  },
  {
   "start": 246.46,
   "end": 247.7,
   "text": "So, but that's another video."
  },
  {
   "start": 248.12,
   "end": 251.28,
   "text": "But that's what I was doing about a week and a half ago."
  },
  {
   "start": 251.4,
   "end": 253.86,
   "text": "I started running every day, and that was nice."
  },
  {
   "start": 254.08,
   "end": 258.96,
   "text": "I finally started running because I just started feeling so much pain, like, in my body."
  },
  {
   "start": 259.46,
   "end": 260.38,
   "text": "Especially in my arm."
  },
  {
   "start": 260.42,
   "end": 265.0,
   "text": "And I thought maybe it was, like, astrophy pain, but it could have been from, like, compression, too."
  },
  {
   "start": 265.06,
   "end": 269.34,
   "text": "Because I'd be doing work on my computer or laying my belly with, like, the big pillow and maybe a little bit of compression on it."
  },
  {
   "start": 269.34,
   "end": 270.9,
   "text": "But, I don't know, carpal tunnel or whatever."
  },
  {
   "start": 272.14,
   "end": 277.48,
   "text": "Anyways, I started to feel, and then I would feel, like, all this energy getting stopped up in me."
  },
  {
   "start": 277.52,
   "end": 278.4,
   "text": "And it was, like, weird."
  },
  {
   "start": 278.5,
   "end": 282.24,
   "text": "Like, I couldn't even hold the mouth steady because my arms started shaking."
  },
  {
   "start": 282.36,
   "end": 283.48,
   "text": "And so I was like, fuck, dude."
  },
  {
   "start": 283.48,
   "end": 284.36,
   "text": "I need to get some exercise."
  },
  {
   "start": 284.36,
   "end": 290.52,
   "text": "So, I started running, and I ran, I think it was, like, 46 minutes or something."
  },
  {
   "start": 290.7,
   "end": 294.08,
   "text": "The last time I did it took me 49 minutes to run four miles."
  },
  {
   "start": 294.2,
   "end": 296.58,
   "text": "It was two miles out, two miles back on this really badass trail."
  },
  {
   "start": 297.62,
   "end": 300.74,
   "text": "Next to a river with fields like this all around."
  },
  {
   "start": 300.86,
   "end": 301.82,
   "text": "And a lake there."
  },
  {
   "start": 302.06,
   "end": 305.88,
   "text": "And a little groundhog colony over here."
  },
  {
   "start": 306.06,
   "end": 307.6,
   "text": "And a dirt trail all the time."
  },
  {
   "start": 308.74,
   "end": 309.7,
   "text": "It was really cool."
  },
  {
   "start": 309.7,
   "end": 314.22,
   "text": "So, yeah, I did that, like, every day."
  },
  {
   "start": 314.3,
   "end": 314.8,
   "text": "That was fun."
  },
  {
   "start": 314.86,
   "end": 315.4,
   "text": "I was getting faster."
  },
  {
   "start": 315.6,
   "end": 319.12,
   "text": "I think I did one in, like, 36, 48, if I remember correctly."
  },
  {
   "start": 320.28,
