  {
   "start": 328.46,
   "end": 329.94,
   "text": "Because I got a vaporizer."
  },
  {
   "start": 331.36,
   "end": 334.8,
   "text": "Yeah, when I came back, I'd just been getting, you know, weed from different places."
  },
  {
   "start": 334.94,
   "end": 337.4,
   "text": "And just been staying high while I do my work on my website."
  },
  {
   "start": 337.4,
   "end": 343.92,
   "text": "And I think it was helping me a lot, too, with the creativity and the grandiose ideas and stuff."
