   "end": 345.0,
   "text": "But I'll talk about that later."
  },
  {
   "start": 345.1,
   "end": 347.34,
   "text": "But I do think it was marijuana-induced."
  },
  {
   "start": 350.54,
   "end": 353.86,
   "text": "Yeah, and also, like, the willingness to put all that detail into it."
  },
  {
   "start": 354.12,
   "end": 359.6,
   "text": "But anyways, but the last months I haven't been listening at all to any audiobook."
  },
  {
   "start": 359.98,
   "end": 361.72,
   "text": "Any MP3 at all."
  },
  {
   "start": 362.58,
   "end": 363.84,
