  },
  {
   "start": 384.48,
   "end": 384.94,
   "text": "For some reason."
  },
  {
   "start": 385.28,
   "end": 386.96,
   "text": "Like, getting myself into some, like, mindset."
  },
  {
   "start": 387.1,
   "end": 389.02,
   "text": "But I would listen to, like, lots of different kinds of music, too."
